'''忘湖'''([[拉丁文|拉丁文]]为"Lacus Oblivionis")是[[月球背面|月球背面]]的一座小[[月海|月海]]，位于[[南极-艾托肯盆地|南极-艾托肯盆地]]内北侧，尺寸为38×24公里。1976年[[国际天文学联合会|国际天文学联合会]]批准采纳了它的命名<ref name=gazetteer>{{cite web
 |url         = http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/3213
 |title       = Lacus Oblivionis
 |work        = Gazetteer of Planetary Nomenclature
 |publisher   = International Astronomical Union (IAU) Working Group for Planetary System Nomenclature (WGPSN)
 |date        = 2010-10-17
 |accessdate  = 2015-06-17
 |archiveurl  = https://www.webcitation.org/67RRi5yN8?url=http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/3213?__fsk=-1744440059
 |archivedate = 2012-05-05
 |deadurl     = no
}}</ref><ref name=Transactions_16B_1977>{{cite book
 |title      =Transactions of the IAU: volume XVIB (Proceedings of the 16th General Assembly of the IAU)
 |url      =https://archive.org/details/proceedingsofsix0016inte
 |author     =E. Müller & A. Jappel
 |publisher  =D. Reidel Publishing Company
 |date       =1977
 |isbn       =90-277-0836-3
 |pages      =[https://archive.org/details/proceedingsofsix0016inte/page/350 350]
}}([http://the-moon.wikispaces.com/IAU+Transactions+XVIB Excerpts]  {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160830075927/http://the-moon.wikispaces.com/IAU%20Transactions%20XVIB |date=2016-08-30 }}; [https://www.webcitation.org/6YikpDLY0?url=http://the-moon.wikispaces.com/IAU+Transactions+XVIB?responseToken=097721a1578f7ec5452abd642e5fcf3ff archive])</ref>。

忘湖“夹在”两座[[陨石坑|陨石坑]]之间：东北40公里的"莫霍洛维奇 R 陨坑"(Mohorovičić R)和西南35公里的"斯尼亚德茨基 Y 陨坑"(Sniadecki Y)，后者也部分被月海[[熔岩|熔岩]]覆盖，月湖中心[[月面坐标|月面坐标]]为{{Coord|20.4|S|168.5|W|globe:Moon}}<ref name=gazetteer/>。

忘湖中部较窄，外形不规则，四周环绕着高度0.5-1.5公里的山丘<ref name=JMARS>According to the laser altimeter on the satellite [[月球勘测轨道飞行器|Lunar Reconnaissance Orbiter]], obtained through the program [http://jmars.asu.edu JMARS] {{Wayback|url=http://jmars.asu.edu/ |date=20190122103100 }}</ref>，南侧与"斯尼亚德茨基 Y 陨坑"组成了一道条狭窄的峡谷；忘湖表面最大的地貌特征是一座直径4公里的半岛，其东侧构成了一座陨坑一半的边缘，这些是截止2015年忘湖中已命名的特征<ref>According to [http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov nomenclature guide МАС] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6EOCinkK0?url=http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/ |date=20130213011459 |dateformat=iso }} ([http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/images/Lunar/lac_105_wac.pdf Map] {{Wayback|url=http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/images/Lunar/lac_105_wac.pdf |date=20190929184959 }})</ref>。

